                    <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Remember your preferences and settings</li>
                        <li>Understand how you use our website</li>
                        <li>Improve our services and user experience</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may limit some functionality of our website.</p>

                    <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
                    <p>We use third-party services that may collect information:</p>
                    <ul>
